summary: The customer is having trouble with their Contoso Wireless product, a model called the Other, and has tried resetting it, checking connections and using different outlets but has not been able to get it to turn on. The agent asked if the customer is using the original power cable that came with the device and the customer confirmed that they are. The agent will now need to ask some additional questions about the product and its setup in order to determine why it is not turning on.
